Anyone can fake
a photograph.

153
00:05:59,693 --> 00:06:00,833
What are you doing?

154
00:06:00,894 --> 00:06:02,464
I am doing a search

155
00:06:02,530 --> 00:06:04,570
to see if our
esteemed senator

156
00:06:04,632 --> 00:06:05,772
from the great state
of California

157
00:06:05,833 --> 00:06:07,743
ever once, once

158
00:06:07,801 --> 00:06:09,801
