170
00:06:29,457 --> 00:06:31,087
So he owes you.

171
00:06:31,158 --> 00:06:33,488
Just get me a meeting.
I'll handle everything
from there.

172
00:06:34,862 --> 00:06:36,332
Okay.

173
00:06:36,396 --> 00:06:38,126
I'll see what I can do.
Thank you.

174
00:06:38,198 --> 00:06:39,498
