244
00:09:33,974 --> 00:09:35,184
Her heart.

245
00:09:35,242 --> 00:09:39,352
It's enlarged 53%
since her last exam.

246
00:09:40,547 --> 00:09:42,347
Her last exam was only
six months ago.

247
00:09:42,415 --> 00:09:44,175
It won't fit.

248
00:09:45,152 --> 00:09:46,352
